	<div itemprop="text"><p>Boy, I wish I you had posted this about six weeks ago when I was struggling with getting my hacked WordPress site up and running again.</p>
<p>I spent considerable amounts of time on it. It was so bad I simply gave up and installed a new database and put it back together post by post in my spare time, which took a week. </p>
<p>I think if I had the info in your post, I would have taken a much different route to revitalization. Of course, then I would not have invested the time into making the site more like I had wanted it in the first place, so there is always good in stuff like this. </p>
<p>Thanks for the honest advice. I have bookmarked your post in case it happens again in the future.</p>
